          "SAMPLE": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                "After  purification, the lead was electrodeposited at a",
                "constant voltage on a cathode composed of a Cu foil",
                "covered with 10mug/cm2 of carbon.  The lead was then",
                "protected with an evaporated carbon layer (15mug/cm2)",
                "and a thin collodion film.  After dissolution of the",
                "copper backing, the target was recovered on an",
                "aluminium  frame and placed in a shielding holder which",
                "fits on the accelerator reaction chamber.",
                "Since the collodion evaporates under the beam, the",
                "final target configuration was C + Pb + C.  The",
                "activity of the 210-Pb isotope:  0.3 GBq."
              ]
            }
          ],
