              "free_text": [
                " Since the gamma-ray spectra observed in singles",
                "were obscured by the large bremsstrahlung background",
                "produced by the radioactive target and by gamma rays",
                "arising from reactions induced on carbon, a",
                "multiplicity filter consisting of an array of 11 NaI",
                "counters was used."
              ]
            }
